summary: KABOKU INU - Welcome to Kaboku inu, the erc-20 project, and the community-driven Japanese meme token on the Ethereum blockchain. and also the perfect combination of kabuso and shikoku. Our goal is to build the newest, hottest, and the most artistic meme-project there ever is. But this won’t be your daily shitcoin. Our hand-made contract is a guarantee that our investors can't be botted and that no whales can't control our supply. Combining a solid contract to a community-driven approach, we're set up for success.
